    <p>For starters, it's actually impossible to eliminate these characters in the sense of banishing them from our mind.</p>
    <p>It's like trying to dissolve a thought. It's impossible to dissolve a thought, because a thought isn't a kind of box we can throw away.</p>
    <p>The truth is that these characters may appear at any time, for any reason.</p>
    <p>All you can do is be aware of which characters you play, and prevent them from becoming </p>
    <p>And through habit, repetition and awareness and you can more-or-less prevent yourself from playing these characters.</p>

    <p>Self-awareness is a very effective approach at dissolving these characters.</p>
  </div>

